Binary change: library.zip
==========================

Purpose
-------
Allow Quivi's bundled pyfreeimage wrapper to start with FreeImage 3.18.0.
FreeImage 3.18.0 exports WebP support, but it removed the legacy
_FreeImage_RotateClassic@12 export that Quivi binds during startup.

Changed file
------------
library.zip

Backup
------
backups/library.zip.before-rotateclassic-binding-patch.bak

